"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-10-breakout-stars-2024-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Has there ever been a more fun Olympics than what we just witnessed in Paris?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 77, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 71, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1166910632794817e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more fun Olympics\", \"from\": 20, \"to\": 39}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These Olympic Games had everything that fans could hope for \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 high drama, dramatic upsets, and athletes willing to push themselves to the absolute limit in the pursuit of greatness.\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These Olympic Games\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 high drama\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 152}, {\"ngram\": \"dramatic upsets\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"the absolute limit\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"the pursuit\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The end result was spectacular, and the Paris Games managed to leave us wanting more even after 17 days of wall-to-wall sports greatness.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The end result\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"17 days\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"wall\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For as magical as the host city was, though, when f