_team\", \"score\": 0.9962313013697757, \"rank\": 0.0037524678371948167, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His individual all-around gold\", \"from\": 8501, \"to\": 8531}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 8550, \"to\": 8555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oka is one of only six athletes to win at least three golds and at least four medals in Paris.\", \"from\": 8569, \"to\": 8663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8657, \"end\": 8662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1166910632794817e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oka\", \"from\": 8569, \"to\": 8572}, {\"ngram\": \"only six athletes\", \"from\": 8583, \"to\": 8600}, {\"ngram\": \"at least three golds\", \"from\": 8608, \"to\": 8628}, {\"ngram\": \"at least four medals\", \"from\": 8633, \"to\": 8653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's quite literally the gold standard in men's gymnastics right now, and a reminder of how far the U.S. needs to go to reach the top.\", \"from\": 8664, \"to\": 8798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold standard\", \"from\": 8685, \"to\": 8702}, {\"ngram\": \"men's gymnastics\", \"from\": 8706, \"to\": 8722}, {\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 8738, \"to\": 8748}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 8760, \"to\": 8768}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 8790, \"to\": 8797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shinnosuke with all of his medals!\", \"from\": 8800, \"to\": 8834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shinnosuke\", \"from\": 8800, \"to\": 8810}, {\"ngram\": \"his medals\", \"from\": 8823, \"to\": 8833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"!pic.twitter.com/PTxAv2a90