lity\", \"from\": 13391, \"to\": 13406}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay events\", \"from\": 13410, \"to\": 13426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Few runners can compete at a world-class level in the 100m and 400m, but Thomas was part of the gold medal-winning relay team at each distance.\", \"from\": 13428, \"to\": 13571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13501, \"end\": 13507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9961940377634558, \"rank\": 0.002150900755857339, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Few runners\", \"from\": 13428, \"to\": 13439}, {\"ngram\": \"a world-class level\", \"from\": 13455, \"to\": 13474}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 13478, \"to\": 13486}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 13512, \"to\": 13516}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal-winning relay team\", \"from\": 13520, \"to\": 13553}, {\"ngram\": \"each distance\", \"from\": 13557, \"to\": 13570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 100m, her third leg split of 10.25 gave Richardson the chance to catch and pass Great Britain for the win.\", \"from\": 13572, \"to\": 13685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13619, \"end\": 13629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7769483908717688e-21, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 13659, \"end\": 13672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999965565334775, \"rank\": 3.4434788016425514e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 13575, \"to\": 13583}, {\"ngram\": \"her third leg split\", \"from\": 13585, \"to\": 13604}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 13630, \"to\": 13640}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 13677, \"to\": 13684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 400m, Thomas and Team USA posted the second-fastest time ever, literally running away from the field to win with ease.\", \"from\": 13686, \"to\": 13811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13699, \"end\": 13705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9961940377634558, \"rank\": 0.002150900755857339, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 13710, \"end\": 13718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.494564733227402e-15, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 13689, \"to\": 13697}, {\"ngram\": \"the second-fastest time\", \"from\": 13726, \"to\": 13749}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 13784, \"to\": 13793}, {\"ngram\": \"ease\", \"from\": 13806, \"to\": 13810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So many athletes that prevailed in Paris have spent their entire lives in pursuit of that success, often sacrificing most other things in their lives as collateral damage.\", \"from\": 13813, \"to\": 13984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13848, \"end\": 13853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1166910632794817e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra